@* 
   Client-side unobtrusive validation scripts.

   This UI package intentionally ships without jQuery/jQuery Validate to keep the
   RCL lightweight. Server-side validation still works.

   If you want client-side validation, add these static assets under:
     wwwroot/lib/jquery-validation/
     wwwroot/lib/jquery-validation-unobtrusive/
   (or switch to CDN includes in this partial).
*@

